productAttributes.productDescription:
From a very humble beginning back in 1997 till today, Arihant has come a long way to become a pioneer in the competitive books market. We have aimed to be the companion of the aspirants guiding them through the hardships and helping them achieve their goals. With our meticulously designed books and magazines, we have conquered the No. 1 position amongst the publishers of competitive, recruitment and entrance exams books in India. And now is the time we take a big leap in a new direction to make it easier than ever for the aspirants with Learning Resources packed in a Compact Disk CD.

The first endeavor in this new segment of learning and practice resources targets JEE Main aspirants. Arihants Test Series for JEE Main is a complete practice cum assessment program aimed at making the aspirants ready to face the exam with confidence.

An examination like Joint Entrance Exam JEE Main which witnesses lakhs of aspirants competing for a handful of seats, requires both hard work and smart work. And to be one of those who get a seat in the college of their choice, one must be thorough with the concepts covered under the syllabi as well as the preparation level and weak & strong areas. To help aspirants achieve perfection of concepts and self analyze their level of preparation, Arihant has come up with an innovative tool in the form of Test Series for JEE Main which will help aspirants in real practice and assessment of their preparation for JEE Main.

This new series has been prepared in the similar format as that of JEE Main Online incorporating number of elements to cover each and every aspect of preparation and assessment for JEE Main. This is an Online cum Offline program which can be attempted in both the formats. CD given with the package is compatible with arihanttestprep.com where it can be attempted online using same credentials as while installing the CD, otherwise it can be attempted in offline format. The package also comes with a Free Revision Booklet covering the entire syllabi of JEE Main 2015.

Highlights of the new Test Series for JEE Main -
  • 175 Topic Tests
    Giving you practice along with assessing your knowledge at Topical Level
  • 90 Chapter Tests
    Making you confident about your knowledge of whole JEE Main Syllabus
  • 24 Unit Tests
    Covering questions from the group of chapters covered in a particular unit
  • Class XI & XII Based Tests
    Questions from syllabus of Class XI & XII
  • 15 Mock Tests
    Giving you Real Practice along with Time Management for JEE Main
  • Previous Year's Solved Papers
    Last 13 year's 2002 - 2014 Solved Papers to give you the exact picture of JEE Main
  • Analysis Reports
    Multiple Analysis Reports - Strong & Weak Topics, Time Taken to attempt the questions, etc
About the Author

An editorial team of highly skilled professionals at Arihant, works hand in glove to ensure that the students receive the best and accurate content through our books. From inception till the book comes out from print, the whole team comprising of authors, editors, proofreaders and various other involved in shaping the book put in their best efforts, knowledge and experience to produce the rigorous content the students receive. Keeping in mind the specific requirements of the students and various examinations, the carefully designed exam oriented and exam ready content comes out only after intensive research and analysis. The experts have adopted whole new style of presenting the content which is easily understandable, leaving behind the old traditional methods which once used to be the most effective. They have been developing the latest content & updates as per the needs and requirements of the students making our books a hallmark for quality and reliability for the past 15 years.
